  "original_title": "Another man was arrested with Tear Gas Ammo",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Another man was arrested with Tear Gas Ammo",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Sri Lanka Police arrested a 30-year-old man from Maligawa Road in Ethul Kotte for the possession of one Tear Gas Ammo.",
        "Sri Lanka Police said that on the 13th of July 2022, a group of police officers was transporting tear gas ammo in a three-wheeler belonging to the Public Peace Management Range during the protest that was taking place at the Polduwa Junction.",
        "A statement from Sri Lanka Police said that protestors had stolen several tear gas ammo during the protest.",
        "The suspect was produced to the Hultsdorf Number 4 Magistrate's Court on Thursday (28) and was remanded to the 5th of August."
      ],
